  "rationale": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice A is correct. It&rsquo;s given that the banner&rsquo;s length <math alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi>\n</math>, in inches, is <math alttext=\"24\"><mn>24</mn>\n</math> inches longer than its width, in inches. It follows that the banner&rsquo;s width, in inches, can be represented by the expression <math alttext=\"x minus 24\"><mrow>\n<mi>x</mi>\n<mo>-</mo>\n<mn>24</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math>. The area of a rectangle is the product of its length and its width. It's given that the area of the banner is <math alttext=\"2,661\"><mn>2,661</mn>\n</math> square inches, so it follows that <math alttext=\"2,661 equals x left parenthesis x minus 24 right parenthesis\"><mrow>\n<mn>2,661</mn>\n<mo>=</mo>\n<mrow>\n<mi>x</mi>\n<mfenced>\n<mrow>\n<mi>x</mi>\n<mo>-</mo>\n<mn>24</mn>\n</mrow>\n</mfenced>\n</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</math>, or <math alttext=\"2,661 equals x squared minus 24 x\"><mrow>\n<mn>2,661</mn>\n<mo>=</mo>\n<mrow>\n<msup>\n<mi>x</mi>\n<mn>2</mn>\n</msup>\n<mo>-</mo>\n<mrow>\n<mn>24</mn>\n<mi>x</mi>\n</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</math>. Subtracting <math alttext=\"2,661\"><mn>2,661</mn>\n</math> from each side of this equation yields <math alttext=\"0 equals x squared minus 24 x minus 2,661\"><mrow>\n<mn>0</mn>\n<mo>=</mo>\n<mrow>\n<msup>\n<mi>x</mi>\n<mn>2</mn>\n</msup>\n<mo>-</mo>\n<mrow>\n<mn>24</mn>\n<mi>x</mi>\n</mrow>\n<mo>-</mo>\n<mn>2,661</mn>\n</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</math>. Therefore, the equation that represents this situation is <math alttext=\"0 equals x squared minus 24 x minus 2,661\"><mrow>\n<mn>0</mn>\n<mo>=</mo>\n<mrow>\n<msup>\n<mi>x</mi>\n<mn>2</mn>\n</msup>\n<mo>-</mo>\n<mrow>\n<mn>24</mn>\n<mi>x</mi>\n</mrow>\n<mo>-</mo>\n<mn>2,661</mn>\n</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice B is incorrect and may result from representing the width, in inches, of the banner as <math alttext=\"24 minus x\"><mn>24</mn><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi></math>, rather than <math alttext=\"x minus 24\"><mrow>\n<mi>x</mi>\n<mo>-</mo>\n<mn>24</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice C is incorrect and may result from representing the width, in inches, of the banner as <math alttext=\"x plus 24\"><mrow>\n<mi>x</mi>\n<mo>+</mo>\n<mn>24</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math>, rather than <math alttext=\"x minus 24\"><mrow>\n<mi>x</mi>\n<mo>-</mo>\n<mn>24</mn>\n</mrow>\n</math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice D is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>",
